:640px;margin:0;border-radius:0;padding:58px 20px 0}.home-app h2{font-size:51px}.home-app-object{width:275px;height:330px;margin:45px auto 0}.app-phone{right:18px;width:166px;height:300px}.app-note{left:0;bottom:36px}.app-phone em{width:93px;margin-top:24px}}
